<p>Hereâ€™s a bit of the recall code. This first snippet is a method called <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">parse_results</code> from a class called Results that lives in lib/models. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">parse_results</code> performs a grep search with an instance variable called <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">query</code> (yes, Iâ€™ve hard-coded my flatiron directory in for now).</p>

